# Force LF line endings on checkout regardless of platform/git config.
# Windows runners default to core.autocrlf=true, which silently rewrites
# committed LF files to CRLF on checkout - broke the golden-file report
# tests (tests/fixtures/report_expected.{csv,json}) comparing our
# LF-only program output against a CRLF fixture. Everything in this repo
# is text; there are no binary assets to exclude.
* text=auto eol=lf
